<br>
Level 56 with Regen3 and Phantom Armor = 14hp/tic. <br>
Level 56 unbuffed, no regen = 6hp/tic i believe.<br>
<br>
Phantom Armor is a level 52 store-bought spell that adds 5hp/tic regen. Takes 4 Cats Eyes as a reagent.<br>
<br>
Regen3 is a General Type AA ability that adds 3 hp/tic regen. It's fairly easy to get, you just need to dedicate time for the 3 AA points.<br>
